ZH: 外婆是我最亲爱的家人。
EN: My grandmother is my dearest family member.

ZH: 我和外婆常常一起做饭。
EN: I often cook with my grandmother.

ZH: 外婆每天早上都给我做早餐。
EN: My grandmother makes breakfast for me every morning.

ZH: 外婆的笑容让我感到温暖。
EN: My grandmother's smile warms my heart.

ZH: 每年过年我都会去外婆家。
EN: I go to my grandmother's house every Chinese New Year.

ZH: 外婆总给我讲很多有趣的故事。
EN: My grandmother always tells me many interesting stories.

ZH: 我很怀念外婆家的味道。
EN: I miss the taste of my grandmother's cooking.

ZH: 外婆教我怎样做中国菜。
EN: My grandmother teaches me how to cook Chinese dishes.

ZH: 外婆的红烧肉是我最爱吃的。
EN: My grandmother's braised pork belly is my favorite.

ZH: 外婆总是给我带一些好吃的零食。
EN: My grandmother always brings me some delicious snacks.

ZH: 我每次去外婆家都喜欢玩她的猫咪。
EN: I always enjoy playing with my grandmother's cats when I visit her.

ZH: 有一次我和外婆一起去了动物园。
EN: Once, my grandmother and I went to the zoo together.

ZH: 我和外婆有时会一起去买菜。
EN: Sometimes my grandmother and I go grocery shopping together.

ZH: 我的外婆已经九十岁了。
EN: My grandmother is already ninety years old.

ZH: 我非常感谢外婆对我的关爱。
EN: I am very grateful for my grandmother's love.

ZH: 外婆总是给我买漂亮的衣服。
EN: My grandmother always buys me pretty clothes.

ZH: 我想和外婆一起学习如何织毛衣。
EN: I want to learn how to knit with my grandmother.

ZH: 我的外婆是我榜样。
EN: My grandmother is my role model.

ZH: 我的外婆喜欢在花园里种花。
EN: My grandmother enjoys planting flowers in her garden.
